import PageHeader from '../../../components/PageHeader/PageHeader'; import axios from 'axios'; import EmbeddedCalendar from "../../../components/EmbeddedCalendar"; import { getDashboard } from '../../../actions/businessDasboardAction'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import styles from './Calendar.css'; import { FooterContainer } from '../../../containers/footer'; import { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; const calendar = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [userProfile, setUserProfile] = useState(null); const [initialized, setInitialized] = useState(false); const [dashboardTotals, setData] = useState(null); useEffect(() => { if (!userProfile) { setUserProfile(JSON.parse(window.localStorage.userProfile)); } if (userProfile && dashboardTotals) { // We have everything initialized setInitialized(true); console.log({dashboardTotals}) } const dashboard = async() => { const businessId = JSON.parse(window.localStorage.userProfile).id const dashboardInfo = await getDashboard(businessId); console.log("dashboardInfo: ", dashboardInfo); setData(JSON.parse(dashboardInfo)); } if(!dashboardTotals){ dashboard(); } }, [userProfile, window.localStorage.userProfile, dashboardTotals]); return initialized ?
